{"tid":1784514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年經。為兒子送上15年來第一餐聖誕大餐","createTime":"2019-12-15T17:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T17:47:26.000Z","uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f562d447a348c408da90117cb3df85cf9acdd1c","tid":1784514,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/20111230/yaa1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F20111230%2Fyaa1.htm&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=6497ab79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F20111230%2Fyaa1.htm&h=55d8f5f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/20111230/yaa1.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】繼去年明益你「夢想成真」，為兩名讀者達成心願後，今年聖誕我們繼續送暖，為讀者陳先生一家實現聖誕願望：「15年來，幾乎從沒帶兒子外出食聖誕大餐，希望給兒子一個特別難忘的聖誕。」表面看來，陳家跟一般小康之家無異，卻又背負?多個不足為外人道的重擔，這是現時不少中產家庭的寫照。生活從來不易，總是一闊三大，尤其在佳節舉家外出食餐好，對不少家庭來說還是個付不起的夢想。明益你聯同The<br />\nMira酒店，為陳家於今年聖誕節送上免費自助晚餐，讓他們為2011年畫上圓滿的句號。<br />\n<br />\n陳基棠先生任職銀行電腦部 System Manager，太太是認證機構秘書，育有一名中四兒子，是不折不扣的小康之家，但背負的生活重擔，往往讓陳先生慨嘆「錢總是不知所終」。兩人正供養三個老人家，由於兩人均在職，需請家傭照顧；又為兒子請來兩名補習老師，加上學習長笛及參加童軍活動，都是陳家重要支出。<br />\n<br />\n但最大的負擔，莫過於供一層位於港島東的七百多呎自住單位，佔收入約三分之一，即使三口之家月入數萬元，七除八扣後還是所剩無幾，實在是啞子吃黃蓮。難怪精打細算的陳太表示，每年最多只能與兒子食自助餐一兩次，並選擇價錢較低廉的午餐時段，至於較平時貴幾成的聖誕大餐，對他們一家來說是過於奢侈的消費：「一家三口連車費，動輒數千。」<br />\n<br />\n夾心中產「有苦說不清」<br />\n<br />\n因此每年聖誕，陳家都與親友在家搞派對，親身下廚以減低開支。但兒子畢竟已15歲，陳生還是希望能讓他一嘗在聖誕樹和熱鬧的節日氣氛下，享受一頓豐富大餐，令兒子有個幸福難忘的回憶，於是便去信明益你參加「夢想成真」活動，寫上這個心願。<br />\n<br />\n「知道獲選後，第一時間告訴兒子，他還不斷跟身邊朋友說今年聖誕要出尖沙嘴食buffet呢。」看兒子首次坐在聖誕樹下，享受自助餐盛宴而展現出燦爛笑容，應該是陳生陳太今年最好的聖誕及新年禮物吧！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"98b0d9073b482678932677ac47f2245f2505673f","tid":1784514,"uid":259010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:13:09.000Z","msg":"真係好撚慘喎 Dlgh"},{"pid":"51e34181d7e42c67d534167f827cec9ac4d75a0d","tid":1784514,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推，今日既行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnDkzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnDkzda.jpg&h=97bc3868&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PxUG26w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxUG26w.jpg&h=5e518208&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFiQbZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFiQbZT.jpg&h=b0320f4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d7003622ece7c79562dee2951fe0294cfe02da3","tid":1784514,"uid":259010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"[quote]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08hwaf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08hwaf3.jpg&h=404b5056&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xOJ85JJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxOJ85JJ.jpg&h=23b3b63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i40.tinypic.com/2lo6n1g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi40.tinypic.com%2F2lo6n1g.jpg&h=acdfb593&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.littleoslo.com/cnt/home/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/winner-612x920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.littleoslo.com%2Fcnt%2Fhome%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F12%2Fwinner-612x920.jpg&h=0481e142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"083bd6690b1bfbe2047558b63bfa70dd35ea8457","tid":1784514,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"咪開垃圾po"},{"pid":"ba75d92ee6f5d15fc75aed570ccda842d2d3aaeb","tid":1784514,"uid":79170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"應該孫都抱埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}